Personal Project that enables me to scrape the HTML content found on an online site, and allow me to convert it into a KEPUB format and downlaoding it onto my Computer as a KEPUB, which can then be transferred onto a Kobo device.
Currently, this code only works on sites where the correct identifiers are selected for the desired content, and likely should be modified if different sites have to be scraped.
Requires the installation of the Calibre app, the path to the application must be modified to match the code.

I do not condone scraping sites illegally, this is only for personal use, on sites that permit web scraping.
